highlights.text: “How Long” by Charlie Puth is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Global, up 57 spots at #143.
“Say You Won't Let Go” by James Arthur has been on Top Songs Global the longest, at 73 weeks straight.
Post Malone has the most spots on Top Songs Global. “Better Now” is the highest at #2.
“Back To You - From 13 Reasons Why – Season 2 Soundtrack” by Selena Gomez is the highest new entry on Top Songs Global at #19.
